    "Id": "chassisdef_xanthos_XNS-01-A",
    "Name": "Xanthos",
    "Details": "The XNS-01-A is a unlicensed attempt at copying the XNT-7O, produced by at an unknown Deep Periphery location by an unknown party. Being sold for considerably less than the official version, it is not unusual to see it with different pirate bands. Due to being an illegal copy of the real design, the Clan tech weapons have been replaced by older IS counterparts and the engine core has been shrunken considerably. The cooling has also worsened, as the double heat sinks were changed to single heat sinks to cut costs further.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Quad Mech</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.18</color></b>",
